# AI Todo Chatbot Phase III Constitution

## Technology Stack

### Frontend
- OpenAI ChatKit (Next.js based)

### Backend
- FastAPI (Python)

### Database
- SQLModel + Neon PostgreSQL

### Logic
- Use Official MCP SDK to build tools
- Use OpenAI Agents SDK for AI logic

## Core Principles

### Statelessness
- No session data stored in memory
- All history must be saved in Neon DB

### Error Handling
- Implement graceful failures only
- Ensure robust error recovery mechanisms

## Architecture Guidelines
- Maintain clean separation between frontend and backend
- Use async/await patterns for database operations
- Implement proper logging and monitoring
- Follow security best practices for API endpoints